  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Creative (Videographer/Photographer)",
  "description": "<p><strong>The role</strong></p>\n<p>UNIFORM is looking for someone who's energetic (yes, our projects can get quite physical), talented with graphic design, photography, digital imaging and visual communication with an interest in marketing and keenly interested in lifestyle, food, fashion and the visual arts.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Photography, Videography and Digital Imaging</li>\n  <li>Communications, Content Creation, Public Relations &amp; Marketing Support</li>\n  <li>Social Media platform management</li>\n  <li>Assist in research and conceptualisation of projects, including production of presentation materials</li>\n  <li>Coordinate and liaise with our clients and collaborators</li>\n  <li>Assist on Shentonista and client photo shoots</li>\n  <li>For fresh graduates, you will undergo an initial internship period prior to being offered a full-time position.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Attained a tertiary education in Photography, Videography or other Creative fields</li>\n  <li>Keen interest in Design, Social Media, Content, Photography, Video Production and editing</li>\n  <li>Excellent with Adobe Creative Suite</li>\n  <li>Proficient in iWork</li>\n  <li>Energetic and outdoor-friendly</li>\n  <li>A good appreciation and understanding of all things visual</li>\n  <li>Well-mannered with excellent communication skills</li>\n  <li>A good team player but also great at working independently</li>\n  <li>Driven, passionate and committed when it comes to personal learning and growth</li>\n  <li>Any experience in accounts servicing or marketing would be beneficial</li>\n  <li>Able to start work immediately</li>\n  <li>Friendly with fluffy furballs; Corgi included</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you are interested, send your CV and portfolio to us.</p>\n<p>Send your application to:<strong> greetings@theuniform.com.sg</strong></p>\n<h4>Additional Application Instructions</h4>\n<p>Please upload only text-based CVs (.doc or .pdf, max 5MB) and include a link to visual portfolios in your CV.</p>",
